channel.title: [SOLVED] Robgob's Control Panel HELP
channel.description:
https://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/google/tutorials/320061-pi-adding-my-control-panel-your-server.html So I've followed all of the steps until I get to: then search for: code: 'public void destruct() {' I can NOT find this anywhere. I checked several files (obv. including client.java and Config.java) Now if you scroll down a bit you can see 'public void initialize() {' which I can't find either. Any help?
EDIT: Solved. For those of you that need help too, absolutely NO code gets edited in the Client. All of it will and should be in Source/Server. And my mistake was that there were TWO .java files of the same name in different spots. The one you will get stuck on is in: XXX/src/server/model/players
